{"tid":752291,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(裝修專家請進）浴室寶有煙味問題","createTime":"2018-07-22T16:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T16:38:01.000Z","uid":36027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"492f387336ce7f8fb566cc0b4c8938bb94f1fead","tid":752291,"uid":36027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"家住和諧式居屋 廁所有一個窗對外<br />\n以前未換浴室寶時 <br />\n如果一般屋企聞到有煙味就係由廚房開左果個窗飄入 閂左就冇野<br />\n但而加換左浴室寶 成日久唔久就有煙味飄入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭以為係浴室寶抽左樓下啲煙味上黎<br />\n於是試過全日熄左個浴室寶 <br />\n(廁所個窗係長期閂實）<br />\n啲煙味都係照攻入黎 <br />\n勁到陣味好似有人係廁所食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n研究左好耐都諗唔到係邊度飄入黎<br />\n其實係咪個浴室寶啲玻璃膠封唔好？<br />\n係咪要換返抽食扇先搞得掂？<br />\n<br />\n有冇工程大佬知道點搞先掂？<br />\n麻煩哂各位 唔該哂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c992d3824989665c611494f039d14bddd10e8b74","tid":752291,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"樓主最好盡快搬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af75f099a52134247d8e5965992d40d882ae97c5","tid":752291,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc07da30b577a59a21a592da506938f0a49ed1a","tid":752291,"uid":36027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c992d3824989665c611494f039d14bddd10e8b74","tid":752291,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"樓主最好盡快搬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:38:01.000Z","msg":"應該附近有人食煙"}]}